":1593666589,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":72523,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":12354,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 20也是错的。。。","timestamp":1593666602,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":72524,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":12354,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 哦，你说15分钟，那就对","timestamp":1593666620,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":72560,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":12354,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我来扮演一下小白!这是为什么啊?20只怎么做到的","timestamp":1593667104,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":72573,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":12354,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"log5(1000000)不应该是9只吗，如果毒水和普通水混合以后不论浓度都会死的话","timestamp":1593667423,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":72595,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":12354,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"https://www.zhihu.com/question/60227816/answer/1274071217","timestamp":1593667818,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":72624,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":12354,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Grace: 对我刚也想说这不是知乎上的么","timestamp":1593668477,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":72791,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":12354,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re : 把这100w只猪分别编号0~999999，然后转化为二进制码，那么二进制码就有$[log_2 1000000]+1$位，然后取来相同数量的猪，第i只猪喝第i位是1的水$(i\\in[0,[log_2 1000000]])$即可","timestamp":1593672824,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":72813,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":12354,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我感觉应该是34只？\n首先应该是可以测4次（因为测量中间没有办法可以得到别的信息所以只能等着）\n如果给这些水编号的话就应该有100w种可能性\n如果每次都有n头猪喝水（所有水平均分）的话就会有n种情况，喝了四次之后n^4种情况，至少要比100w大才可以\n100w^0.25=31.6，所以应该是32，32，32，31，每次死一头之后别的猪可以重复利用所以应该是34头？","timestamp":1593673311,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":72878,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":12354,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"2^（n+n-1+n-2+n-3）\u003e10^6，n=7？","timestamp":1593674843,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":73443,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":12354,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Jason: 答案上面有了。。。9只","timestamp":1593688119,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":5,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":12354,"reply":19,"tag":null,"text":"# 问：\n\n一百万桶水中一桶有毒，猪喝毒水后15内任意时刻死。至少要多少只猪才能一个小时内求出哪一桶有毒？\n\n请给出喝水方案并证明该方案为最优解。","timestamp":1593666031,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782588,"url":"","vote":{}}}